title: Danger Zone (1951 Film-Noir) Sax Heist & Yacht Party Coverup - directed by William Berke

sources.title: Danger Zone (1951 Film-Noir) Sax Heist & Yacht Party Coverup - directed by William Berke
sources.description:
San Francisco PI, Dennis O'Brien (Hugh Beaumont) is hired to bid on a valuable saxophone and escort Vicki Jason (Pamela Blake) to a yacht party. But when a murder occurs aboard, O'Brien finds himself framed and must uncover the killer among the scheming guests to clear his name!

Alternative title: Pier of Peril / Pier 23 (1951)

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/boHXZrzKTq8


Director: William Berke
Writers: Herb Margolis, Lou Morheim, Julian Harmon
Actors: Hugh Beaumont, Edward Brophy, Pamela Blake 
Genres: Crime, Drama, Film Noir, Mystery, Romance, Thriller
Release date: April 20, 1951
